        "text": "<p>CS Flair was born from a passion for preserving ancient jewelry-making traditions while infusing them with contemporary aesthetics. Each piece in our collection is handcrafted by skilled artisans who have inherited techniques passed down through generations.</p><p>We believe that true luxury lies in the imperfections of the handmade, the story behind every curve and contour, and the connection between the creator and the wearer.</p>",
